Package org.apache.soap.encoding.soapenc

Class Summary
ArraySerializer A ArraySerializer can be used to serialize and deserialize arrays using the SOAP-ENC encoding style.
Base64  
Base64Serializer A Base64Serializer is used to serialize and deserialize byte arrays using the SOAP-ENC encoding style.
BeanSerializer A BeanSerializer can be used to serialize and deserialize JavaBeans using the SOAP-ENC encoding style.
BooleanDeserializer This deserializer can be used to deserialize something into a boolean.
BooleanObjectDeserializer This deserializer can be used to deserialize something into a Boolean.
ByteDeserializer This deserializer can be used to deserialize something into a byte.
ByteObjectDeserializer This deserializer can be used to deserialize something into a Byte.
CalendarSerializer This class de/serializes instances of java.util.GregorianCalendar from/to the XML-Schema type 'date'.
DateSerializer This class de/serializes instances of java.util.Date from/to the XML-Schema type 'timeInstant'.
DecimalDeserializer This deserializer can be used to deserialize something into a double.
DoubleDeserializer This deserializer can be used to deserialize something into a double.
DoubleObjectDeserializer This deserializer can be used to deserialize something into a Double.
FloatDeserializer This deserializer can be used to deserialize something into a float.
FloatObjectDeserializer This deserializer can be used to deserialize something into a Float.
FPDeserUtil FPDeserUtil: Utilities to help with deserialization of floating point special values.
HashtableSerializer A HashtableSerializer can be used to serialize and deserialize Hashtables using the SOAP-ENC encoding style.
IntDeserializer This deserializer can be used to deserialize something into an int.
IntObjectDeserializer This deserializer can be used to deserialize something into an Integer.
LongDeserializer This deserializer can be used to deserialize something into a long.
LongObjectDeserializer This deserializer can be used to deserialize something into a Long.
MapSerializer A MapSerializer can be used to serialize and deserialize Maps using the SOAP-ENC encoding style.
MimePartSerializer A MimePartSerializer can be used to serialize Java's InputStream, JavaMail's MimeBodyPart and Java Activation Framework's DataSource and DataHandler objects from/to multipart Mime attachments to the SOAP message.
ParameterSerializer A ParameterSerializer is used to serialize and deserialize parameters using the SOAP-ENC encoding style.
QNameSerializer A QNameSerializer serializes a QName as follows: ns:QNameLocalPart
ShortDeserializer This deserializer can be used to deserialize something into a short.
ShortObjectDeserializer This deserializer can be used to deserialize something into a Short.
SoapEncUtils These static methods can be used to do much of the repetitive and mechanical work that is required when generating structures using the SOAP-ENC encoding style.
StringDeserializer This deserializer can be used to deserialize something into a String.
UrTypeDeserializer An UrTypeDeserializer deserializes xsd:ur-type objects, but right now only deals with nulls.
VectorSerializer A VectorSerializer can be used to serialize (but not deserialize) Vectors and Enumerations using the SOAP-ENC encoding style.
